toxml

Interface IXMLElement

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    XMLElement

    public interface IXMLElement
    IXMLElement abstracts the tree structure of XML. The interface supports only the basic operations. There is no support for namespaces in elements as well as in attributes, as they are not required.
    Author:
    Harsh Jain
